    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3267010/extras/b30bfd3686eba5f00fce3fb1571676a2.avif?t=1757698326\" width=800 height=333 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Annie's School Trip is a game about a young student called Annie. She has a field trip to go along with the other students fom her school. While she was exploring the new area she ends up doing something wrong... Now a big threat is coming for her.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3267010/extras/021ac61fae615cff9652dc9ad21af30a.avif?t=1757698326\" width=800 height=333 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This game is a sidescroller platformer horror game. You need to get to the other side of the screen avoiding the obstacles. The game also has some comedy and dark humor stuff in it.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The game contains:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A lot of levels to go through, jumping over the holes.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >comedy and dark humor.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >scary situations.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >some boss fights.</p></li></ul>",
